"type":"text"},{"text":"‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and subclasses sport a customizable energy management system.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Since scanners running on a live video feed can put a lot of load onto the CPU and\/or GPU","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the device, causing the battery to drain quickly and running the device hot, you can customize the energy","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"consumption using this class by configuring the rate of detections\/recognitions per second in performance mode as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"well as in energy saving mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In performance mode the scanners will be fed with a higher, configurable rate of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"video frames per second.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"After a certain, configurable period of inactivity the energy save mode will be engaged and the rate","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of scans will be reduced to a lower (configurable) rate."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You can also configure the time of inactivity before the automatic mode switches from performance to energy save mode."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Inactivity here means that both of the following conditions are met:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"role":"symbol","title":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"symbol"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration/init":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/init","abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/init","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"init"}},"variantOverrides":[{"patch":[{"path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK~1SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/title","op":"replace","value":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"},{"path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK~1SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/fragments","op":"replace","value":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}]},{"path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK~1SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/navigatorTitle","op":"replace","value":[{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}]}],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}]}